# A tiny single-triangle OBJ for the assimp ImportSource backend test.
# 3 unique positions, 1 face, CCW winding. assimp triangulates (already
# triangles) and normalizes the sidecar .mtl into an ImportMaterial.
# Used by assimp_source_test (Task 10).

mtllib tri.mtl
o tri
v 0.0 0.0 0.0
v 1.0 0.0 0.0
v 0.5 1.0 0.0
vt 0.0 0.0
vt 1.0 0.0
vt 0.5 1.0
vn 0.0 0.0 1.0
usemtl tri_mat
f 1/1/1 2/2/2 3/3/3
